headline: Universal Robots unveils UR8 Long: Engineered to tackle the most demanding and space-constrained automation tasks
summary: Universal Robots (UR), the world's leading collaborative robot (cobot) company, today introduced a new addition to its portfolio, the UR8 Long, at FABTECH in Chicago. The long-reach industrial collaborative robot is available for order now, with shipping to begin in October.

headline: Teradyne (TER) Stock Declines While Market Improves: Some Information for Investors
summary: In the closing of the recent trading day, Teradyne (TER) stood at $118.9, denoting a -1.08% move from the preceding trading day.
